FREEMAN
v.
STATE of NC, et al. 273P17-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 1, 2017 Jacqueline Freeman, for Freeman, Jacqueline. Grayson Kelley, Chief Deputy, for State of N.C., et al.
